Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.request

package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.request
This package contains classes responsible for constructing and sending HTTP requests to the Roboflow API. It includes functionality for performing both synchronous and asynchronous API requests for various image processing tasks such as classification, segmentation, and object detection. The request senders in this package handle the communication with the server and the conversion of request and response data.
